HEADWORD: Neuroskeleton
<hw>Neu`ro*skel"e*ton</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Neuro-</ets> + <ets>skeleton</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Anat.)</fld>
<def>The deep-seated parts of the vertebrate skeleton which are in
